Interface SimpleExerciseMaterialUploader.ExerciseMaterialUploadSuccessListener

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
Enclosing class:
SimpleExerciseMaterialUploader
public static interface SimpleExerciseMaterialUploader.ExerciseMaterialUploadSuccessListener
extends java.io.Serializable

Implementors of this interface can be registered to a SimpleExerciseMaterialUploader through #registerSuccessListener(ExerciseMaterialUploadSuccessListener) registerSuccessListener(). Registered listeners will be informed with the newly added ExerciseMaterial after a successful upload.

Author:
Riku Haavisto

Method Detail

materialUploadSucceeded

void materialUploadSucceeded(ExerciseMaterial newMaterial,
                             java.lang.String fileName,
                             java.lang.String mimeType)

After a successful upload in SimpleExerciseMaterialUploader this method is called for all registered SimpleExerciseMaterialUploader.ExerciseMaterialUploadSuccessListeners with the newly added ExerciseMaterial.

Remember that added ExerciseMaterials are not yet saved!

Parameters:
newMaterial - the newly added ExerciseMaterial
fileName - the name of the uploaded file
mimeType - the mimeType of the uploaded file
